# Testing controller

## Things to test

Emergency switch

### I2C bus

- Pressure sensors (2x)
- External I2C for Ferris wheels (14x)
- External I2C device (2x)

### SPI0 bus

- Main valve (1x): Needs 12V plugged in, and either at least one valve connected or a multimeter to measure 12V
- Horizontal buttons (16x)

- Switches (8x) and LEDs (6x) 
    At boot, cycle through all LEDs
- Vertical buttons (16x)

- Potentiometers (2x)

- TFT screen (1x)

- External GPIO expander (1x)

### SPI1 bus
Motor valves (16x): Needs 12V plugged in, and either at least one valve connected or a multimeter to measure 12V


